{"tid":1943033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"N號房存在藝人奴隸","createTime":"2020-03-25T11:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T19:04:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c9ea13d71c2dfbc0f83ef31b00741927ff3c43","tid":1943033,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006Py7Fagy1gd6bz9uy6rj30o41hcn59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006Py7Fagy1gd6bz9uy6rj30o41hcn59.jpg&h=9a8ba341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會員用戶：​&ldquo;奴隸中有現職偶像嗎?&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n趙主彬：&ldquo;有&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n趙主彬以藝人非法攝影物為誘餌招攬收費會員，表示:&ldquo;在收取150萬韓元入場費的高額房間裡可以看到名人的高水準視頻。&rdquo;部分會員如果懷疑是不是真正的藝人視頻，就會將藝人的身份證號碼和住址等個人信息上傳到網上獲得信任。<br />\n<br />\n趙主彬主張說，在藝人中也有不能違背自己拍攝並提供性剝削物的所謂&ldquo;奴隸&rdquo;，特別是有10多歲未成年藝人的視頻，只要交錢進入高額房間，從去年12月到今年1月，趙主彬在談話中提到的藝人達10多人。 &ldquo;抓住10多歲女歌手的弱點，將其馴服為奴隸&rdquo;，並揚言說自己還保留著著名女子組合成員B某出道前的視頻。"},{"pid":"d3685c162ffc1945e8384f97e4bf45626676c882","tid":1943033,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"知你想講邊個"},{"pid":"a1eb1f89710b3b75c7a901a8bb913a65d7281d4a","tid":1943033,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3685c162ffc1945e8384f97e4bf45626676c882","tid":1943033,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"知你想講邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"我都唔知你點知"},{"pid":"c35ce34d5e0d43679b732ff292068de3e655bb7b","tid":1943033,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:53:24.000Z","msg":"呢個仆乖快能啲落地獄🙏🏻"},{"pid":"f57cc748fb7964e9a4b736f576cac723a2c1863d","tid":1943033,"uid":249766,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c35ce34d5e0d43679b732ff292068de3e655bb7b","tid":1943033,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:53:24.000Z","msg":"呢個仆乖快能啲落地獄🙏🏻"},"ci